      <section eId="sec_CCP-5001">
        <num>CCP 5001</num>
        <heading>Section </heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-5001__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>An appeal from a judgment rendered by a parish court or by a city court shall be
taken to the court of appeal.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-5001__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Appeal shall be on the record and shall be taken in the same manner as an appeal
from the district court.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112134</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
